UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Hi Felnok! My studies in the Burning Steppes are proceeding splendidly. And I owe $N a lot for all $ghis:her; help! Here\'s what I need to continue: A steelcoil bumber-bitzel A 17-gauge ice-spanner 12 pounds of duck feathers A jar of that glue you make Thanks a lot Felnok, and when we see each other again remind me not to put coal in your boots! -Tinkee' WHERE entry=1710; /* text: Hi Felnok! My studies in the Burning Steppes are proceeding splendidly. And I owe $N a lot for all $ghis:her; help! Here\'s what I need to continue: A steelcoil bumber-bitzel A 17-gauge ice-spanner 12 pounds of duck feathers A jar of that glue you make Thanks a lot Felnok, and when we see each other again remind me not to put coal in your boots! -Tinkee */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Here lies King Terenas Menethil II -- Last True King of Lordaeron. Great were his deeds -- long was his reign -- unthinkable was his death.          "May the Father lie blameless for the deeds of the son.           May the bloodied crown stay lost and forgotten." ' WHERE entry=1750; /* text: Here lies King Terenas Menethil II -- Last True King of Lordaeron. Great were his deeds -- long was his reign -- unthinkable was his death.          "May the Father lie blameless for the deeds of the son.           May the bloodied crown stay lost and forgotten." */
UPDATE locales_page_text SET text_loc8='Throm-Ka, warrior. I won\'t fawn over your deeds of strength and valor. They\'re old news. Killed any humans lately? Not many, I wager. You\'re slowing down. Getting soft without a challenge. I need another pair of hands, and no matter what your toadies say, you need the training I can give you. Whenever you get that through your thick skull, I\'ll be waiting under the canopy just outside the Den. -Frang, Warrior Trainer ' WHERE entry=2150; /* text: Throm-Ka, warrior. I won\'t fawn over your deeds of strength and valor. They\'re old news. Killed any humans lately? Not many, I wager. You\'re slowing down. Getting soft without a challenge. I need another pair of hands, and no matter what your toadies say, you need the training I can give you. Whenever you get that through your thick skull, I\'ll be waiting under the canopy just outside the Den. -Frang, Warrior Trainer */
